Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001835_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-03-22\" src=\"ISic001835_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001835.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-03-22\" src=\"ISic001835-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001835_left_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-03-22\" src=\"ISic001835_left_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001835_left.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-03-22\" src=\"ISic001835_left-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Dimartino: ΔΒ; Kaibel ΔΙ// (intended to illustrate damage to the right of the vertical); lapis: the surface is lost to the right of a vertical stroke, compatible with e.g. Β also\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>of Philisto D[-]\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>It is not possible to say whether the final letter is an Iota or another letter beginning with a vertical, given the damage to the stone. It is possible that this bore same ΔΒ as on ISic001834; but Β, Γ, Ε, Η, Ι, Κ, Μ, Ν, Π, Ρ are all theoretically possible.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 59.1132 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> De Spuches 1864 13 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002042\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002042\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">437.4\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hoffmann 1904 5233 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dimartino 2009 722 no. e \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001364\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001364\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dimartino 2017 testo e \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002579\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002579\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> \u003Cp> Types list: \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Λ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Λ type2\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"